# Comunica RDF/XML RDF Parse Actor

A comunica RDF/XML RDF Parse Actor.

This module is part of the [Comunica framework](https://github.com/comunica/comunica).

## Install

```bash
$ yarn add @comunica/actor-rdf-parse-rdfxml
```
